Achievement titles are special public titles earned by unlocking
achievement tiers.

They are separate from your normal player title. Equipping an
achievement title does not overwrite your regular title text.

Use:

  achievements titles
      Lists your unlocked titles and shows the exact command for each one.

  atitle <title-id>
      Equips a title you have unlocked.

  atitle clear
      Removes your equipped achievement title.

Examples:

  atitle slayer:bronze
  atitle locksmith:silver

If you are not sure what the id is, do not guess. Run:

  achievements titles

That output shows the exact command to use.

See also: help achievements, help atitle, help leaderboard
